remarks  CYS have been generated
remarks  PATCH ZN  reference=1=( atom a 20 * ) 
remarks            reference=2=( atom b 30 * )
remarks            reference=3=( atom a 11 * )
remarks            reference=4=( atom b 22 * )
remarks   END

PRESidue ZNK     { disulfide bridge  ...CYS      CYS...
                                              \DISU/            }
 GROUP     
  MODIfy ATOM 1CB           CHARge= 0.19  END
  MODIfy ATOM 1SG  TYPE=S   CHARge=-0.19  END
